{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "2.680", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "2.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.560", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.240", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "10.480", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kinder zu haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "10.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.400", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist f\u00fcr viele Menschen in Deutschland das Wichtigste und Sch\u00f6nste im Leben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.320", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00dcber 90\u00a0Prozent der 18- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "19.520", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bis 30-J\u00e4hrigen geben in Umfragen an, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "19.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.200", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ein Kind oder auch mehrere Kinder haben zu wollen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.080", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber l\u00e4ngst nicht alle k\u00f6nnen ihren Kinderwunsch verwirklichen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.160", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "jedenfalls nicht ohne medizinische Unterst\u00fctzung."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.160", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mehr als 6\u00a0Millionen Menschen in Deutschland sind ungewollt kinderlos, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.640", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und die Zahl steigt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "38.240", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "L\u00e4ngere Ausbildung und h\u00e4ufige Jobwechsel f\u00fchren dazu, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "38.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.800", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sich Menschen heute immer sp\u00e4ter daf\u00fcr entscheiden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "42.160", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kinder zu bekommen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "42.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "43.520", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "viele so sp\u00e4t, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "43.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.600", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sie Hilfe ben\u00f6tigen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "54.080", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Unterst\u00fctzung f\u00fcr Ma\u00dfnahmen der k\u00fcnstlichen Befruchtung haben SPD und Gr\u00fcne 2004 aber stark reduziert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "54.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.440", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was vorher als Regelleistung zu 100\u00a0Prozent von der GKV \u00fcbernommen wurde, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "61.480", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wird seitdem nur noch zur H\u00e4lfte von der Kasse bezahlt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "61.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "63.400", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber nur f\u00fcr die ersten drei Versuche, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "63.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "68.840", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nur bei Ehepaaren und nur f\u00fcr Frauen zwischen 25 und 40\u00a0Jahren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "68.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "76.960", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die schwarz-gelbe Bundesregierung hat die finanzielle Unterst\u00fctzung mit einer Richtlinie des BMFSFJ zur F\u00f6rderung der assistierten Reproduktion erleichtert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "76.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "81.440", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mittlerweile f\u00f6rdert diese Richtlinie auch unverheiratete Paare."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "81.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "82.400", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Unser Ansatz war, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "82.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "85.840", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Bund und L\u00e4nder gemeinsam ein Viertel der Gesamtkosten tragen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "85.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "87.320", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "unter der Voraussetzung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "87.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "90.600", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sich die L\u00e4nder parit\u00e4tisch beteiligen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "90.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "92.560", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir Freie Demokraten geben offen zu: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "92.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "94.720", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir waren da zu optimistisch. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "94.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "102.080", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Lediglich f\u00fcnf ostdeutsche Bundesl\u00e4nder und das Land Niedersachsen haben entsprechende Richtlinien erlassen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "102.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "106.400", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die vom Bund zur Verf\u00fcgung gestellten Mittel werden nicht vollst\u00e4ndig ausgesch\u00f6pft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "106.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "108.520", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil die L\u00e4nder nicht mitziehen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "108.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "114.320", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Erf\u00fcllung eines Kinderwunsches ist dadurch in hohem Ma\u00dfe abh\u00e4ngig vom Wohnort derjenigen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "114.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.080", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die ein Kind bekommen m\u00f6chten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "118.560", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese Ungleichbehandlung halten wir f\u00fcr absolut falsch."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "118.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "129.320", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Als Freie Demokraten setzen wir uns bereits seit Jahren in den L\u00e4ndern daf\u00fcr ein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "129.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "132.280", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Finanzierung der Kinderwunschbehandlung zu verbessern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "132.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "139.080", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In Hamburg beispielsweise gab es entsprechende Initiativen meiner damaligen Fraktion 2013 und 2016. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "139.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "149.320", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sowohl in Schleswig-Holstein als auch in Nordrhein-Westfalen ist die Kofinanzierung des Bundesprogramms durch das Land Teil des Koalitionsvertrags mit unseren Partnern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "149.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "153.880", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bundesweit einheitliche Regelungen sind dennoch in weiter Ferne. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "153.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "157.000", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Hier besteht dringender Handlungsbedarf."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "157.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "165.640", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Abh\u00e4ngigkeit der F\u00f6rderungsbereitschaft des Wohnsitzbundeslandes ist aber nur ein Teil des Problems. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "165.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "168.800", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Unverheiratete Paare erhalten keine F\u00f6rderung durch die Krankenkasse, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "168.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "172.440", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber unter Umst\u00e4nden durch die BMFSFJ-Richtlinie. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "172.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "174.720", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Alleinstehende gehen komplett leer aus, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "174.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "174.960", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und das, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "174.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "180.400", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "obwohl inzwischen jedes dritte Kind in Deutschland au\u00dferhalb einer Ehe geboren wird. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "180.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "183.120", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Lesbische Paare werden gar nicht gef\u00f6rdert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "183.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "188.160", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Entscheidet sich ein Paar zu fr\u00fch oder zu sp\u00e4t im Leben f\u00fcr eine Wunschkindbehandlung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "188.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "190.080", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bleibt die Unterst\u00fctzung aus. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "190.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "196.360", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Besonders problematisch ist das schlagartige Ende der F\u00f6rderung der Frauen ab dem 40.\u00a0Lebensjahr."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "196.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "198.440", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zum Stichwort \u201eSocial Freezing\u201c: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "198.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "200.960", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die k\u00fcnstliche Befruchtung mit eingefrorenen Ei- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "200.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "207.200", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Samenzellen wird weder von GKV noch durch die BMFSFJ-Richtlinie gef\u00f6rdert."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "207.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "213.920", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der von uns vorgelegte Antrag ist ein erster pragmatischer und hoffentlich schnell umzusetzender Schritt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "213.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "218.560", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um Menschen mit Kinderwunsch besser zu unterst\u00fctzen und zu helfen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "218.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "220.560", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "unabh\u00e4ngig vom Wohnort und vom Familienstand."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "220.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "222.720", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nur am Rande und ganz kurz: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "222.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "232.280", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Davon unbenommen brauchen wir in Deutschland eine weitergehende Diskussion, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "232.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "239.960", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bei wem wir dar\u00fcber hinaus eine assistierte Reproduktion unterst\u00fctzen wollen und welche Ma\u00dfnahmen dabei zum Einsatz kommen sollen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "239.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "247.760", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aus unserer Sicht sollten Eizellspende und nicht kommerzielle Leihmutterschaft unter bestimmten Bedingungen legalisiert werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "247.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "253.280", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Daf\u00fcr muss jedoch sehr viel mehr ge\u00e4ndert werden als nur die Richtlinie des BMFSFJ, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "253.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "256.280", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "an der wir mit dem vorliegenden Antrag ansetzen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "256.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "260.120", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir arbeiten aber an weiteren entsprechenden Initiativen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "260.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "261.040", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "261.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "262.320", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es ist offensichtlich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "262.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "268.880", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die bestehenden F\u00f6rderinstrumente der Lebenswirklichkeit der Menschen in unserem Land nicht gerecht werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "268.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "271.880", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Lassen Sie uns daher einen ersten wichtigen Schritt machen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "271.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "273.640", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich freue mich auf die Debatte."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "273.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "274.840", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "274.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "278.440", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Kollegin Suding.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "278.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "285.240", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Als N\u00e4chster f\u00fcr die CDU/CSU-Fraktion der Kollege Stephan Pilsinger. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "285.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "289.000", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch f\u00fcr ihn ist es seine erste Parlamentsrede."
   ]
  }
 ]
}